Decorator to start a child span under the existing current transaction.
If there is no current transaction, then nothing will be traced.

```{code-block}
:caption: Usage

import sentry_sdk

@sentry_sdk.trace
def my_function():
    ...

@sentry_sdk.trace
async def my_async_function():
    ...
```
